&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 5 Staff Nurse - Elective Orthopaedics (Redlands Ward)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a motivated and enthusiastic band 5 staff nurse to join the nursing team on Redlands Ward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Redlands is a 30 bedded ward, which is part of a ring fenced unit providing care for elective orthopaedic patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will have an interest in caring for orthopaedic patients, and will be focused on driving forwards enhanced recovery pathways, and improvements in nursing care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be committed towards providing support for student nurses, as well as managing their own ongoing personal development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sister Helen Slade on 0118 322 7485 or helen.slade@royalberkshire.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
